            <div class=""sub_stand_out"">
                <h3 class=""small_heading""> II. 1. Origin of the /program   </h3>
                <p class=""description""> 
                    The current evolution of companies in a very fierce competitive environment is no longer to be demonstrated. In this way, communication plays
                    a vital role in any modern organization, since it is the essential link that ensures the company’s good visibility and ensures daily competition in
                    the market in which it operates. As these two elements are indispensable for the proper functioning of any national and international organization,
                    it is undeniable for us, to include a program of corporate communication, ");
            WriteLiteral(@"based mainly on current business needs. The course programme
                    consists of providing future communication managers with unparalleled skills.	      
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class=""sub_stand_out"">
