                <h3 class=""smaller_heading""> II.2.1. General objective </h3>
                <p class=""description""> 
                    The aim of this programme is to train multi-talented graduates in the media and business communication professions, particularly with a strong
                    knowledge of the communication field. At the end of this program, graduates will be able to put to use the skills acquired in different
                    communication firms; and also assist and accompany companies in their communication campaign.                        
                </p>

                <h3 class=""smaller_heading""> II.2.2. Specific Objectives </h3>
  ");
