                </p>
                <ul class=""one_list"">
                    <li> Assist and support companies in mastering its communication issues, </li>
                    <li> Work with communication agencies; companies and public and private media, </li>
                    <li> Develop budgets for the communication, </li>
                    <li> Hold a position of Marketing Manager, </li>
                    <li> Press Secretary. </li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class=""small_heading""> II.3. Program approach   </h3>
